---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = "The Profoundness Framework";
const description = "Explore your life's purpose and personal growth journey with our comprehensive framework.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-gray-800">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            The <span class="text-orange-500">Profoundness</span> Framework
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            {description}
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Framework Overview -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="lg:text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl mb-12">
            Understanding the Framework
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left">
            <p>
              The Profoundness Framework is a comprehensive approach to personal development that helps individuals navigate their journey toward deeper meaning and fulfillment. It's built on three core concepts, each with three key aspects that work together to create a balanced and purposeful life.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Concept 1: Self-Discovery -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. The Journey of Self-Discovery</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-indigo-500 mx-auto"></div>
        </div>
          
        <!-- Subsection 1 -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[400px]">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10092288/pexels-photo-10092288.jpeg?" alt="Person in self-reflection" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Discovering Your Core Values</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                The journey of self-discovery begins with understanding your fundamental beliefs and principles. These core values serve as your internal compass, guiding your decisions and shaping your identity. When you align your life with these values, you experience greater authenticity and fulfillment.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                This process involves deep introspection and honest self-assessment. It's about identifying what truly matters to you, beyond societal expectations or external validation. As you uncover these values, you'll find they provide clarity in times of uncertainty and help you make choices that resonate with your true self.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                Living in alignment with your core values creates a sense of integrity and purpose. It's the foundation upon which you can build a life that feels meaningful and true to who you are at your core.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
          
        <!-- Subsection 2 -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse min-h-[400px]">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10092288/pexels-photo-10092288.jpeg?" alt="Person journaling" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Rewriting Your Personal Narrative</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                The stories we tell ourselves shape our reality. Your personal narrative influences how you perceive yourself and your place in the world. By examining and rewriting limiting beliefs, you can transform your self-perception and unlock new possibilities.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                This process involves becoming aware of the subconscious scripts that may be holding you back. As you identify these patterns, you can consciously choose to replace them with empowering beliefs that support your growth and potential.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                Crafting a new narrative isn't about denying your past, but rather about interpreting it in a way that serves your highest good. It's a powerful act of self-creation that can lead to profound personal transformation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
          
        <!-- Subsection 3 -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[400px]">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10092288/pexels-photo-10092288.jpeg?" alt="Person in nature" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Embracing Your Strengths</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Each of us possesses unique strengths and talents that make us who we are. Identifying and embracing these qualities allows you to operate from a place of natural ability and confidence. When you focus on your strengths, you not only excel but also experience greater joy and fulfillment in your endeavors.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                This journey of self-discovery involves recognizing both your innate talents and the skills you've developed over time. It's about understanding how these strengths can be applied in various aspects of your life to create meaningful impact.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                By embracing and developing your unique combination of strengths, you can make your most valuable contributions to the world while experiencing deep personal satisfaction and growth.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Concept 2: Mindful Awareness -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Cultivating Mindful Awareness</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-teal-500 mx-auto"></div>
        </div>
          
        <!-- Subsection 1 -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[400px]">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10092288/pexels-photo-10092288.jpeg?" alt="Person meditating in nature" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Power of Presence</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                In our fast-paced world, the ability to be fully present has become a rare and valuable skill. Mindful awareness brings you into the current moment, allowing you to experience life more deeply and respond to situations with clarity rather than reacting out of habit or emotion.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                This practice isn't about emptying your mind, but rather about observing your thoughts and feelings without judgment. As you cultivate this awareness, you'll notice greater focus, reduced stress, and an enhanced ability to appreciate the simple joys of everyday life.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                The present moment is where life truly happens. By learning to anchor yourself here, you'll find a wellspring of peace and wisdom that's always available, no matter what challenges you face.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
          
        <!-- Subsection 2 -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse min-h-[400px]">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10092288/pexels-photo-10092288.jpeg?" alt="People in deep conversation" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Emotional Intelligence</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Emotional intelligence is the foundation of meaningful relationships and effective communication. It begins with self-awareness—recognizing your own emotions as they arise—and extends to understanding and empathizing with the feelings of others.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                As you develop this skill, you'll find it easier to navigate conflicts, build stronger connections, and maintain emotional balance during challenging situations. Emotional intelligence isn't about suppressing feelings, but rather about understanding them and responding in ways that serve your highest good and that of those around you.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                This awareness creates a bridge between your inner world and the world around you, fostering deeper connections and more authentic relationships in all areas of your life.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
          
        <!-- Subsection 3 -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[400px]">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10092288/pexels-photo-10092288.jpeg?" alt="Person enjoying nature" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Sensory Awareness</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Our senses are powerful gateways to the present moment. By consciously engaging with what we see, hear, touch, taste, and smell, we ground ourselves in the here and now. This practice can transform ordinary experiences into moments of wonder and appreciation.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Sensory awareness helps quiet the constant chatter of the mind, offering a direct path to presence. Whether it's feeling the warmth of sunlight on your skin, savoring the flavors of a meal, or listening to the sounds of nature, these simple acts can become profound practices in mindfulness.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                As you cultivate this awareness, you'll discover that joy and beauty are always available in the present moment, waiting to be noticed and appreciated.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Concept 3: Purposeful Action -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Taking Purposeful Action</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-indigo-500 mx-auto"></div>
        </div>
          
        <!-- Subsection 1 -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[400px]">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10092288/pexels-photo-10092288.jpeg?" alt="Person planning goals" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Crafting Your Vision</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                A clear vision acts as your North Star, guiding your decisions and keeping you aligned with your deepest values and aspirations. It's not just about setting goals, but about creating a compelling picture of the life you want to build—one that excites and motivates you to take consistent action.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                This vision should be flexible enough to evolve with you, yet specific enough to provide clear direction. When your daily actions are informed by this vision, even small steps become meaningful progress toward the life you truly desire.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                Remember, a powerful vision isn't just about what you want to achieve, but more importantly, about who you become in the process of pursuing it.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
          
        <!-- Subsection 2 -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse min-h-[400px]">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10092288/pexels-photo-10092288.jpeg?" alt="Person working on habits" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Power of Habit</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Our lives are shaped by our habits—the small, consistent actions we take every day. By intentionally designing habits that align with your values and goals, you create a framework for sustainable success and personal growth.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                The key to effective habit formation lies in starting small, being consistent, and focusing on the process rather than just the outcome. When you build habits that are enjoyable and meaningful, they become easier to maintain over time.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                Remember that every action you take is a vote for the person you wish to become. With each small, consistent step, you're not just building habits—you're building your future self.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
          
        <!-- Subsection 3 -->
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[400px]">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10092288/pexels-photo-10092288.jpeg?" alt="People making an impact" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Creating Meaningful Impact</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                True fulfillment comes not just from personal success, but from making a positive difference in the lives of others. When you align your actions with a purpose larger than yourself, your work takes on deeper meaning and significance.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Impact doesn't always require grand gestures. Often, it's the small, consistent acts of kindness, generosity, and service that create the most meaningful ripple effects. By focusing on how you can contribute value to others, you'll find that your own life becomes richer and more purposeful.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                In the end, the legacy we leave is not measured by what we accumulate, but by the positive impact we have on the people and world around us. When you live with this awareness, every action becomes an opportunity to create meaningful change.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-12">
          How the Framework Works
        </h2>
        <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-lg">
            The Profoundness Framework isn't a one-size-fits-all solution but rather a flexible guide that adapts to your unique journey. Here's how you can apply it:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-4 mt-6">
            <li><strong>Assessment:</strong> Begin by evaluating your current state across the four pillars.</li>
            <li><strong>Goal Setting:</strong> Identify areas for growth and set meaningful objectives.</li>
            <li><strong>Implementation:</strong> Apply the framework's principles through daily practices.</li>
            <li><strong>Reflection:</strong> Regularly assess your progress and adjust your approach.</li>
            <li><strong>Evolution:</strong> As you grow, the framework evolves with you, offering new insights and challenges.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="bg-orange-600 dark:bg-orange-700">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:py-16 lg:px-8 lg:flex lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
          <span class="block">Ready to explore the framework?</span>
          <span class="block text-orange-100">Start your journey today.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-8 flex lg:mt-0 lg:flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="inline-flex rounded-md shadow">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-orange-600 bg-white hover:bg-orange-50">
              Get Started
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
